				<td colspan="2"><span>Remember though, it is good for if you need to heal.  The healing portion of your mana song does work.
<br />

<br />
KEI gives you a bigger mana pool to work with, once it is filled up.  So, while it does not help regen your mana faster, it does help by giving you a bigger possible mana pool.
<br />

<br />
Tribute regen counts towards worn regen.
<br />
Worn regen works.
<br />

<br />
No songs, buffs, mana dumps, nor modrod work for us to regen mana faster.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
